1
00:00:33,100 --> 00:00:34,960
If you wear shoes that do not fit,

2
00:00:35,400 --> 00:00:37,060
you could easily fall.

3
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:42,200
Do you suspect he is lying,
Commissioner Di?

4
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:50,160
Confess everything now!

5
00:00:51,940 --> 00:00:58,460
=The Tang Mist S1=

6
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:19,100
=Episode 11=

7
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,400
In the end,

8
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,920
you still saw right through me.

9
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:34,600
I have studied
the classics my entire life.

10
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,680
I couldn't take it lying down.

11
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:44,160
I couldn't bear such humiliation.

12
00:02:45,220 --> 00:02:48,540
(Mourning)

13
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,640
Pan'er,

14
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,160
if Zhuang hadn't told me

15
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,760
that you paid for my mother's medicine,

16
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,780
I would still be kept in the dark.

17
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:01,730
You only married him for my sake.

18
00:03:11,250 --> 00:03:12,100
Pan'er,

19
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,280
no more regrets.

20
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,200
Make a choice for your own sake.

21
00:03:18,700 --> 00:03:19,890
Let's leave this place.

22
00:03:21,390 --> 00:03:22,200
Tonight.

23
00:03:22,850 --> 00:03:23,730
We leave tonight.

24
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,290
The curfew begins at the Xu hour.

25
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:26,640
I will wait for you at Zhuang's.

26
00:03:34,350 --> 00:03:36,160
I am already old and frail.

27
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,280
At my advanced age,

28
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:41,120
I only wanted to marry and have children

29
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,920
to carry on my lineage.

30
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,670
Yes.

31
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,400
I was indeed coveting Gu Pan'er's

32
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,600
youth and beauty.

33
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,700
But I was completely devoted to her,

34
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:57,040
and I never once wronged her.

35
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,000
I never expected

36
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,050
things to end so miserably.

37
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,490
The night she returned,

38
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,040
I killed her.

39
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:17,880
Then I hid her body

40
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:19,540
at the theater troupe,

41
00:04:21,530 --> 00:04:23,070
framing Zhuang Luobai for it.

42
00:04:25,770 --> 00:04:27,440
To cover up the truth,

43
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,120
I killed her mother.

44
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:36,920
And to eliminate
any remaining loose ends,

45
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:39,360
I killed that miserable gambler.

46
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,480
Buying and selling women

47
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,640
is already a grave offense.

48
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,280
Yet you doubled down

49
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,000
on your errors,

50
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,480
taking three human lives.

51
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:47,720
It is utterly

52
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,080
monstrous and unforgivable!

53
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:53,720
Yes.

54
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,740
I was wrong.

55
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,280
From the very beginning,

56
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:05,680
I was wrong.

57
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:07,960
Prefect Gongsun,

58
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,360
take him away.

59
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,840
Guards!

60
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,560
What is it, Master?

61
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,920
We must have missed something.

62
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:40,020
(Gu Pan'er wanted)

63
00:05:40,111 --> 00:05:41,020
(to give Zhuang Luobai)

64
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,720
(this green robe.)

65
00:05:42,890 --> 00:05:43,660
It must be.

66
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:44,630
(Usually,)

67
00:05:44,650 --> 00:05:47,080
(Zhuang Luobai only wears plain robes.)

68
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:48,960
Why would she give him a green robe?

69
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,320
(This green robe)

70
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:54,110
(was meant for Dong Ling.)

71
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,480
(We kept our eyes on Zhuang Luobai)

72
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,680
(and completely overlooked Dong Ling.)

73
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,600
Since you ask that,

74
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,680
did Hou Guangming kill her?

75
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,480
No.

76
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:11,400
It wasn't Zhuang Luobai
who wanted to kill Hou Guangming.

77
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,600
It's you.

78
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,080
Why wouldn't it be me?

79
00:06:15,090 --> 00:06:16,920
(Hou's Residence)
(He wanted to draw us away)

80
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,400
(to help Dong Ling exact her revenge.)

81
00:06:19,010 --> 00:06:20,950
(The one who truly
wanted to kill Hou Guangming)

82
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,720
(was Dong Ling.)

83
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:26,800
Sir!

84
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:29,170
We found a knife wound
on Hou Guangming's back.

85
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:30,880
Dong Ling is in danger!

86
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,220
Find her!

87
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:38,760
Split up and search!

88
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:49,500
Over here!

89
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,030
The knife wound on Hou Guangming

90
00:06:57,130 --> 00:06:58,510
was from Dong Ling's attack.

91
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,466
But her injuries are more severe.

92
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,511
She can still be saved.

93
00:07:33,550 --> 00:07:34,520
You're awake.

94
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:37,920
Commissioner Di...

95
00:07:38,490 --> 00:07:39,920
Rest easy.

96
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,880
Hou Guangming has confessed.

97
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:44,120
Justice has been served for Gu Pan'er.

98
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:50,080
This is returned to its rightful owner.

99
00:07:55,310 --> 00:07:59,400
♪Drifting snow falls♪

100
00:07:59,780 --> 00:08:03,880
♪Fleeting dreams fly into the flame♪

101
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:11,440
♪This transient life is but a cage♪

102
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:16,810
♪Shattering the chains of fate♪

103
00:08:17,770 --> 00:08:21,730
♪Seeing through the human heart♪

104
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:30,000
♪Life and death,
the grand illusion ends♪

105
00:08:31,900 --> 00:08:36,640
♪Now scattered by heaven and earth♪

106
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,680
Commissioner Di.

107
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,960
I lied to you.

108
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,560
I didn't want Pan'er to be remembered

109
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,800
as a swindler after her death.

110
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:54,120
So I hid the fact that
we had planned to run away together.

111
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,200
That night,

112
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:58,360
I waited in Zhuang's room

113
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,640
until dawn.

114
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:01,640
I thought

115
00:09:01,650 --> 00:09:02,960
she had changed her mind.

116
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:04,880
Little did I know,

117
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,600
she had already met a cruel end
at Hou Guangming's hands.

118
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,120
I wanted to follow Pan'er to the grave,

119
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,444
but I couldn't accept it.

120
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:15,080
Hou Guangming must be behind

121
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:17,000
the deaths of Pan'er and her family.

122
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:20,000
So I went to Zhuang.

123
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,866
I asked him to help me get revenge.

124
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:34,160
I am going to kill Hou Guangming.

125
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:37,000
Whether it's Hou Guangming

126
00:09:37,340 --> 00:09:38,320
or us,

127
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:41,320
the authorities must be
watching our every move.

128
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:43,400
Killing him

129
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,240
will be no easy task.

130
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:49,440
Zhuang,

131
00:09:50,290 --> 00:09:52,120
help me draw the authorities away.

132
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,360
You are a woman.

133
00:09:54,866 --> 00:09:56,880
Do you have the strength
to kill Hou Guangming?

134
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:00,290
Pan'er cannot rest in peace.

135
00:10:01,422 --> 00:10:02,860
How can I stand by and watch you

136
00:10:03,290 --> 00:10:04,450
walk into the lion's den?

137
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:05,720
I must have revenge.

138
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:08,040
Even if it kills me,

139
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,840
I must have it.

140
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:22,960
Put this on.

141
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,360
You become a god.

142
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:31,840
The three of you cherished one another.

143
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:33,960
I am honored to have witnessed

144
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:36,120
such genuine devotion...

145
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,720
What do you think, Master Zhuang?

146
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:53,720
Don't I look

147
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,600
better than you?

148
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:55,440
Yes.

149
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,280
Yes.

150
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:11,680
Master.

151
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:13,600
What on earth is wrong with you?

152
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,600
It's like that woman has bewitched you.

153
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,720
What is this nonsense?

154
00:11:17,390 --> 00:11:19,760
(Zhuang was dragged
into this storm for nothing.)

155
00:11:20,510 --> 00:11:21,750
(I am entirely to blame)

156
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,350
(for his involvement.)

157
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,650
As for

158
00:11:26,690 --> 00:11:28,460
the rumors
about his affair with Gu Pan'er

159
00:11:28,770 --> 00:11:30,360
have been publicly cleared.

160
00:11:30,680 --> 00:11:32,120
Their reputations will be restored.

161
00:11:38,060 --> 00:11:40,820
(One Month Later)

162
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,680
Master.

163
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:47,980
I was wrong.

164
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,600
Master!

165
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:04,060
Where are you?

166
00:12:04,260 --> 00:12:08,820
(Marionette Umbrella Dance)

167
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:40,200
(Luobai,)

168
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:44,290
(you desired nothing more
than to become the Red-Faced Guardian.)

169
00:12:45,740 --> 00:12:48,270
(Today, your wish is granted.)

170
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:04,450
♪Life is a dream♪

171
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:08,860
(Xuansi Drama Troupe)
♪A dream like chasing the wind♪

172
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:13,290
♪Yet I am lost within it,
refusing to wake♪

173
00:13:13,330 --> 00:13:14,970
Wenbo truly is a master puppeteer.

174
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:16,280
Just look at this.

175
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:17,550
This puppet he made

176
00:13:17,620 --> 00:13:18,990
really captures the essence

177
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,440
of Master Zhuang Luobai.

178
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:22,860
It is absolutely lifelike.

179
00:13:23,288 --> 00:13:24,330
The resemblance is uncanny.

180
00:13:24,444 --> 00:13:25,750
It looks just like a real person.

181
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:28,088
Wenbo deserves his reputation
as a master puppeteer!

182
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:30,200
Its build

183
00:13:30,444 --> 00:13:31,850
looks exactly like Master Zhuang.

184
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,120
Indeed.

185
00:13:33,210 --> 00:13:34,280
I couldn't agree more!

186
00:13:45,570 --> 00:13:47,620
Master!

187
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,040
(Ming Yu.)

188
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,870
(For the God-Welcoming Dance,)

189
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:17,950
(you will be the lead dancer.)

190
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:21,940
(The future of this Nuo dance)

191
00:14:23,170 --> 00:14:24,460
(is now entrusted to you.)

192
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,800
(Dance well.)

193
00:14:28,860 --> 00:14:30,390
(Carry the will of the god)

194
00:14:31,355 --> 00:14:33,900
(and guard this path of expelling evil
and upholding justice.)

195
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,000
(Remember,)

196
00:14:40,160 --> 00:14:41,620
(do not fail yourself,)

197
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,400
(and do not)

198
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:47,420
(fail the Nuo opera.)

199
00:14:50,680 --> 00:14:51,650
Master...

200
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,690
I was wrong, Master.

201
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,760
You taught me thousands of times,

202
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,720
yet I still make mistakes onstage.

203
00:14:58,720 --> 00:15:00,090
It's because I am foolish.

204
00:15:00,710 --> 00:15:03,200
Stop punishing yourself like this.

205
00:15:04,230 --> 00:15:05,280
Master...

206
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:22,920
Take it off.

207
00:15:23,680 --> 00:15:24,920
You will find your true self

208
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:27,700
and become who you are meant to be.

209
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:30,160
(But only by)

210
00:15:30,160 --> 00:15:31,590
(shedding your worldly shackles)

211
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:33,880
(and forgetting yourself)

212
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:36,680
(can you perfectly bring her to life.)

213
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:45,640
(In my heart,)

214
00:15:45,640 --> 00:15:46,680
(Master)

215
00:15:47,070 --> 00:15:48,390
(is the Guardian itself.)

216
00:15:49,490 --> 00:15:51,840
One day, you will surpass me.

217
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:54,000
I will be waiting.

218
00:16:00,370 --> 00:16:01,920
Master...

219
00:16:02,760 --> 00:16:04,230
Why did you kill my master?

220
00:16:13,590 --> 00:16:15,440
You must be the disciple

221
00:16:15,980 --> 00:16:18,100
Zhuang Luobai thought
of on his deathbed.

222
00:16:18,710 --> 00:16:20,530
I must avenge my master.

223
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:27,060
I will kill you!

224
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:28,120
Stop!

225
00:16:28,540 --> 00:16:29,770
He didn't kill your master.

226
00:16:33,460 --> 00:16:34,650
The autopsy revealed

227
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:36,800
that your master died
of chronic exhaustion.

228
00:16:37,130 --> 00:16:39,000
You should have killed me just now!

229
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:42,270
You should have killed me.

230
00:16:45,130 --> 00:16:46,690
Why do you seek death so eagerly?

231
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:48,840
What was your connection

232
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:50,150
to Zhuang Luobai?

233
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,920
When I was ten years old,

234
00:16:57,760 --> 00:17:00,110
Luobai and I fled a famine to Raozhou.

235
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,240
Completely alone,

236
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:04,040
we had only each other to rely on.

237
00:17:05,120 --> 00:17:06,520
Later on...

238
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:09,350
(He studied the Nuo opera,)

239
00:17:10,430 --> 00:17:12,220
(while I mastered puppetry.)

240
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:15,650
(Our crafts diverged drastically,)

241
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:19,140
(and we constantly argued
over form and spirit.)

242
00:17:20,310 --> 00:17:21,920
I mocked his obsession,

243
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:24,070
and he chided my arrogance.

244
00:17:25,050 --> 00:17:26,740
We parted ways in anger,

245
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:28,330
and for over ten years,

246
00:17:28,620 --> 00:17:30,580
we never spoke
a single word to each other.

247
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,840
Until two months ago,

248
00:17:34,430 --> 00:17:36,360
that fool suddenly came to see me.

249
00:17:37,470 --> 00:17:38,410
He said

250
00:17:38,770 --> 00:17:40,150
he came to say goodbye.

251
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:43,710
Only then
did I learn he was terminally ill

252
00:17:44,990 --> 00:17:46,690
and that his days were numbered.

253
00:17:51,040 --> 00:17:52,380
Why me?

254
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:55,580
Why me?

255
00:17:56,370 --> 00:17:57,600
For the very first time,

256
00:17:58,330 --> 00:18:00,170
he invited me
to watch the Winter Festival.

257
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:03,000
He said I would see his apprentice

258
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:04,320
dancing with flowing sleeves.

259
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:06,360
Master...

260
00:18:06,840 --> 00:18:08,660
To see how the woman in the script

261
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:11,020
emerges from her cocoon
like a butterfly.

262
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:14,060
It was all an idle wish.

263
00:18:15,630 --> 00:18:17,120
On the day of the Winter Festival,

264
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:19,400
all I saw

265
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:22,280
was him alone in the snow,

266
00:18:23,290 --> 00:18:25,170
taking his final breaths in this world.

267
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:36,710
Luobai.

268
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:39,030
Hold on.

269
00:18:39,670 --> 00:18:40,670
Please, hold on!

270
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,800
I will go get a physician.

271
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:45,440
Wenbo,

272
00:18:46,560 --> 00:18:48,750
you wanted your puppets
to dance just like me.

273
00:18:49,250 --> 00:18:50,680
I have found a way.

274
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:53,820
My soul...

275
00:18:54,310 --> 00:18:55,590
is about to fade.

276
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:59,020
I leave my mortal shell to you.

277
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:02,720
Put it to good use.

278
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:06,040
Promise me.

279
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:11,410
Promise me.

280
00:19:12,120 --> 00:19:12,920
I will.

281
00:19:13,430 --> 00:19:14,430
I will.

282
00:19:52,040 --> 00:19:53,500
Wenbo,

283
00:19:53,640 --> 00:19:54,920
look at that.

284
00:19:57,360 --> 00:19:59,240
The Guardian has come for me.

285
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:01,960
The Guardian has come for me.

286
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:18,000
(All mortal lives are caught in a web,)

287
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,780
(and who can truly be free of burdens?)

288
00:20:20,840 --> 00:20:22,520
(Some are tangled by fame and fortune,)

289
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:25,030
(and others are bound
by the threads of love.)

290
00:20:26,450 --> 00:20:28,400
(But if one can
break free from this cage)

291
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:30,880
(and escape worldly attachments,
even for a moment...)

292
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:34,640
(Even if the trap
is ultimately inescapable,)

293
00:20:34,880 --> 00:20:36,360
(that brief moment of brilliant bloom)

294
00:20:37,020 --> 00:20:39,880
(reveals a soul's truest self.)

295
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:42,280
(So it was for Zhuang Luobai,)

296
00:20:44,760 --> 00:20:45,550
(for Dong Ling,)

297
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,250
(and for Pan'er.)

298
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:52,070
(And so it is for us all.)

299
00:20:52,850 --> 00:20:57,060
♪Fleeting dreams fly into the flame♪

300
00:20:57,480 --> 00:21:04,650
♪This transient life is but a cage♪

301
00:21:06,600 --> 00:21:09,900
♪Shattering the chains of fate♪

302
00:21:10,860 --> 00:21:14,800
♪Seeing through the human heart♪

303
00:21:15,230 --> 00:21:23,220
♪Life and death,
the grand illusion ends♪

304
00:21:25,220 --> 00:21:30,620
(Wangnian County, Raozhou)

305
00:21:35,220 --> 00:21:36,780
(Changsha County, Tanzhou)

306
00:21:38,340 --> 00:21:43,580
(Part Three: The Fox Demon)

307
00:21:47,800 --> 00:21:48,840
Young Lady,

308
00:21:49,320 --> 00:21:50,280
I am terribly parched.

309
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:52,200
Could I trouble you for a bowl of water?

310
00:21:52,560 --> 00:21:53,880
Please, come inside and sit.

311
00:21:54,170 --> 00:21:54,780
Thank you.

312
00:22:18,760 --> 00:22:19,760
Little girl,

313
00:22:20,240 --> 00:22:22,180
would you like some sweet fruit?

314
00:22:22,866 --> 00:22:24,022
On the trees just over there,

315
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:25,960
there are so many sweet fruits growing.

316
00:22:26,130 --> 00:22:27,140
They are delicious.

317
00:22:27,155 --> 00:22:27,850
Let's get some,

318
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:28,822
- shall we?
- Sure.

319
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,910
Have some soup first.

320
00:22:34,670 --> 00:22:35,690
What kind of soup is this?

321
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:40,340
It's your

322
00:22:40,620 --> 00:22:42,150
black-hearted soup.

323
00:22:47,580 --> 00:22:48,700
(Preview of Next Episode)

324
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:03,760
Master,

325
00:23:03,760 --> 00:23:04,920
a report from the Bureau.

326
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,180
The fox demon has struck again.

327
00:23:06,320 --> 00:23:07,560
What I desire

328
00:23:07,560 --> 00:23:09,440
is your heart.

329
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:11,690
Won't you grant me my wish,
Young Master?

330
00:23:19,670 --> 00:23:21,250
♪Night covers the long streets♪

331
00:23:22,330 --> 00:23:24,040
♪The city remains silent♪

332
00:23:25,430 --> 00:23:27,020
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

333
00:23:27,280 --> 00:23:29,520
♪Words still left unspoken♪

334
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:32,560
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

335
00:23:33,690 --> 00:23:36,160
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

336
00:23:36,780 --> 00:23:38,260
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

337
00:23:38,260 --> 00:23:41,400
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

338
00:23:42,020 --> 00:23:43,940
♪Love is born from desire♪

339
00:23:44,630 --> 00:23:46,760
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

340
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:49,560
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

341
00:23:49,560 --> 00:23:52,860
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

342
00:23:54,310 --> 00:23:55,630
♪Someone once warned me♪

343
00:23:55,630 --> 00:23:57,150
♪To stop upon this shore♪

344
00:23:57,150 --> 00:23:58,470
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

345
00:23:58,470 --> 00:23:59,960
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

346
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:01,080
♪If one thought retreats♪

347
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:02,380
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

348
00:24:02,380 --> 00:24:03,720
♪But in this world♪

349
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:06,120
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

350
00:24:07,950 --> 00:24:10,760
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

351
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:12,230
♪Still I walk ahead♪

352
00:24:12,460 --> 00:24:13,680
♪Let it pierce through♪

353
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:18,420
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

354
00:24:18,420 --> 00:24:20,660
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

355
00:24:20,660 --> 00:24:22,060
♪Covering every heart♪

356
00:24:22,060 --> 00:24:23,250
♪How many people♪

357
00:24:23,510 --> 00:24:24,880
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

358
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:27,090
♪Yet call it♪

359
00:24:27,290 --> 00:24:28,630
♪Fate?♪

360
00:24:28,990 --> 00:24:30,170
♪Life and death♪

361
00:24:30,170 --> 00:24:31,430
♪Balanced on a single line♪

362
00:24:31,780 --> 00:24:32,950
♪Light and shadow♪

363
00:24:32,950 --> 00:24:34,210
♪Hanging side by side♪

364
00:24:34,210 --> 00:24:35,690
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

365
00:24:35,690 --> 00:24:37,100
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

366
00:24:37,100 --> 00:24:38,640
♪In the end, it is only♪

367
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,020
♪A single misguided thought♪

368
00:24:40,020 --> 00:24:41,580
♪If unveiling the truth♪

369
00:24:41,580 --> 00:24:42,920
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

370
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:44,090
♪Then this answer♪

371
00:24:44,090 --> 00:24:45,450
♪Can it still remain true?♪

372
00:24:45,450 --> 00:24:46,850
♪When love and law♪

373
00:24:46,850 --> 00:24:48,330
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

374
00:24:48,330 --> 00:24:49,730
♪Which figure before me♪

375
00:24:49,730 --> 00:24:56,930
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

376
00:24:56,930 --> 00:24:59,660
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

377
00:24:59,660 --> 00:25:01,250
♪Still I walk ahead♪

378
00:25:01,250 --> 00:25:02,490
♪Not for fame or glory♪

379
00:25:02,490 --> 00:25:07,360
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

380
00:25:07,360 --> 00:25:09,170
♪Human nature is clouded♪

381
00:25:09,170 --> 00:25:10,890
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

382
00:25:10,890 --> 00:25:12,360
♪Though this world♪

383
00:25:12,360 --> 00:25:13,730
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

384
00:25:13,730 --> 00:25:15,980
♪There is still a light♪

385
00:25:15,980 --> 00:25:18,940
♪Worth pursuing♪

386
00:25:18,940 --> 00:25:20,760
♪Every case has its ending♪

387
00:25:20,760 --> 00:25:22,020
♪But night does not always fade♪

388
00:25:22,290 --> 00:25:23,670
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

389
00:25:23,670 --> 00:25:24,890
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

390
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,240
♪If justice stands♪

391
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:27,490
♪Without mercy beside it♪

392
00:25:27,490 --> 00:25:29,290
♪Then how is it♪

393
00:25:29,290 --> 00:25:38,850
♪Any different from a blade?♪

394
00:25:38,850 --> 00:25:42,040
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

395
00:25:42,040 --> 00:25:43,520
♪Still I walk ahead♪

396
00:25:43,520 --> 00:25:44,910
♪Even if the world♪

397
00:25:44,910 --> 00:25:49,640
♪Refuses to answer♪

398
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:51,600
♪When every hidden truth♪

399
00:25:51,600 --> 00:25:53,310
♪Finally reveals itself♪

400
00:25:53,310 --> 00:25:54,670
♪I only wish♪

401
00:25:54,670 --> 00:25:56,150
♪To hold on♪

402
00:25:56,150 --> 00:26:00,890
♪Within the darkness♪

403
00:26:00,890 --> 00:26:02,890
♪To the heart♪

